  "title": "An oval zigzagging UFO was observed in Curitiba for 1 hour [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/28/an-oval-zigzagging-ufo-was-observed-in-curitiba-for-1-hour-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1ao",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 26th,</strong> 1996. Time: 21h00. Duration: one hour. In Curitiba, State of Paraná, three people spotted an oval UFO, alternating silver, red and blue colors. According to the witnesses, the unknown object was small and zigzagged, moving at &#8220;very fast&#8221; speed. The witness who reported the sighting was unable to estimate the altitude of the sighted UFO, pointing out only that it was &#8220;quite high&#8221;. The event was observed with the naked eye and in &#8220;good weather&#8221;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.432. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Curitiba, Estado do Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
